{"id":274033,"type":1,"name":"T-DRAGON","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/3b/07/274033_1L1P6.jpg","summary":"　　在微观的世界里，等待人类的只有绝望！突如其来的神秘病毒，感染者的死亡率高达百分之九十九。带着这个令人绝望的数字，病毒在日本全土开始蔓延。高中生光太郎的弟弟，也不幸感染了这种病毒。要想救弟弟，就必须捕获携带这种病毒的外星生物——T型异龙。这种据说是唯一拥有病毒抗体的外星生物，身长却只有五厘米。为此，光太郎被缩小后，来到了微观世界中。然而，在这个百分之一的世界里，等待着光太郎和其他搜索队员的只有绝望和恐怖！","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>T型异龙</li><li><span>册数: </span>10</li><li><span>话数: </span>52</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/40453\">桜谷シュウ</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/17734\">小学館クリエイティブ</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8410\">月刊ヒーローズ</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>T-DRAGON【ティードラゴン】</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>ティードラゴン</li><li><span>开始: </span>2015-05-01(2015年6月号)</li><li><span>结束: </span>2019-11-01(2019年12月号)</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"漫画系列","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":40453,"image":"","name":"樱谷秀","desc":"作者"},{"id":17734,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1b/f6/17734_prsn_R0Vr7.jpg","name":"小学馆Creative","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8410,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/13/63/8410_prsn_2eAlL.jpg","name":"月刊HERO'S","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":274034,"name":"T-DRAGON (01)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/46/31/274034_TRup2.jpg"},{"id":274035,"name":"T-DRAGON (02)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/67/ce/274035_85Efm.jpg"},{"id":274036,"name":"T-DRAGON (03)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/9c/15/274036_QdS5H.jpg"},{"id":274037,"name":"T-DRAGON (04)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/75/14/274037_Iss7Z.jpg"},{"id":274038,"name":"T-DRAGON (05)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/04/cf/274038_cvBBq.jpg"},{"id":274039,"name":"T-DRAGON (06)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/fc/8f/274039_l3llA.jpg"},{"id":274040,"name":"T-DRAGON (07)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/06/d8/274040_BggM0.jpg"},{"id":274041,"name":"T-DRAGON (08)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/4e/8d/274041_IvwWE.jpg"},{"id":322889,"name":"T-DRAGON (09)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/59/73/322889_pc